release.notes:
Limited Edition release (5000 units pressed). Exclusive to Metallica.com and special pop-up stores during the 2017 Metallica summer tour. 

From Metallica.com, "Newly mastered for vinyl and mixed by the team that brought you Hardwired…To Self-Destruct, the three-disc limited edition package is pressed on 140-gram vinyl and includes the digital download of the show as well. The set list includes the first ever live performance of “Moth Into Flame” along with 14 other tracks played at the historic theater."
